@(B.21 = 21) @fsux{Ŋišgiŋal} of the @fsux{sa-gida}.

#lg C	sa-jara


@(C.22 = 22-40) @wDN{Enlil}, great lord of the gods, elevated above the numerous people! ……, great lord of the gods, elevated above the numerous people! …… your august utterances are prominent. …… cannot be countermanded, your statements are firm. Decide a good fate …… for the constant attendant of your temple ……. …… @wRN{Išme-@wDN{Dagan}}, the son of @wDN{Enlil}, ……. May …… to the uttermost limits of heaven and earth …… exalted.  ((1 line fragmentary))  May …… submit ……. May you …… @wRN{Išme-@wDN{Dagan}} …….  ((5 lines fragmentary))  May …… be bestowed on you ……. May you …… indefatigable ……. …… holy place, pure place …….

#trailer rubric	sa-jara


@(C.41 = 41) @fsux{Sa-ŋara}.

